to rigid\nlattices, the BCC-FCC-HCP phase diagram is found. For $-2<m<n<0$, the BCC\nlattice is the only energy minimizer. Choosing $-4<m<n<-2$, the FCC and SH\nlatices become minimizers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jul 2021 14:32:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jul 2021 10:01:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 Aug 2021 09:36:54 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 12:56:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
